      • Resource

        public Resource(String uri)
        Constructor. Assumes no angle brackets around the uri like in Nx. Assuming conformance to the spec, which can be achieved e.g. using NxUtil.escapeForNx(String) after URI.toASCIIString().
        See Also:
        The spec

      • Resource

        public Resource(URI uri)
        Constructor. Does some escaping so is possibly not too fast. Escaping is done using NxUtil.escapeForNx(String) after URI.toASCIIString().
